entries.text: the last time i argued with someone was about a month ago and it was with my daughter and i was arguing with her over her therapy she has cancer and she was not telling me enough she was not giving me enough information and so that made me very angry i was frustrated and angry

entries.speaker: ellie
entries.text: yeah

entries.text: i could not function i could not drive i could not sleep i could not eat at my i i could not do anything i was completely shut down i felt like i felt like i was looking out a window and and life was going on outside that window and i was just stuck i behind the glass i i could not participate
